OL,3,CCharity boss warns of dire famine in
OL,4,CEthiopia
OL,6,FThere are signs that an impending
OL,7,Fcatastrophe caused by famine is
OL,8,Funfolding inaccording to a charity
OL,9,Fleader.
OL,11,FWidespread starvation in the war-
OL,12,Fdamaged nation has left the founder of
OL,13,FMary's Meals, Magnus MacFarlane-
OL,14,FBarrow, urging for immediate action to
OL,15,Fbe taken.
OL,17,FThe charity has been serving school
OL,18,Fmeals in Ethiopia since 2017.
