OL,3,CCharity boss warns of dire famine in
OL,4,CEthiopia
OL,6,FThe organisation's CEO said: "It's as
OL,7,Fextreme as anything I've ever
OL,8,Fwitnessed in terms of the current
OL,9,Fsuffering and the potential for more
OL,10,Fdeterioration, unless there is a
OL,11,Fsignificant intervention".
OL,13,FTwo years of civil war is believed to
OL,14,Fhave claimed the lives of more than
OL,15,F600,000 people.
OL,17,FIn addition, millions of people have
OL,18,Fbeen displaced and infrastructure and
OL,19,Fhealth services destroyed.
