OL,3,CCharity boss warns of dire famine in
OL,4,CEthiopia
OL,6,FThis is evident in the region's
OL,7,Fhospitals, where Mary's Meal's say it
OL,8,Fhas spoken to doctors who claim they
OL,9,Fare seeing up to three times' more
OL,10,Fchildren dying from malnutrition,
OL,11,Fresulting in a mortality rate around
OL,12,Ffive times higher than normal.
OL,14,FThe severity of what is happening in
OL,15,FEthiopia is going largely unreported,
OL,16,Faccording to the charity, because
OL,17,Fjournalists are struggling to gain
OL,18,Faccess to the region.
