OL,3,CCharity boss warns of dire famine in
OL,4,CEthiopia
OL,6,FWhile schools have been closed during
OL,7,Fthe conflict, providing meals in
OL,8,Feducational facilities has been
OL,9,Fpaused, but Mary's Meals has been
OL,10,Fserving meals to thousands of people
OL,11,Fin refugee camps.
OL,13,FMr MacFarlane-Barrow said it's hard to
OL,14,Fexaggerate just how serious the
OL,15,Fsituation is in Tigray.
OL,17,F"People are already dying of hunger
OL,18,Fand everything we're hearing on the
OL,19,Fground points to a well-founded fear
OL,20,Fof much worse to come if the world
OL,21,Fdoesn't respond.
